data.description:
PRICE REDUCED: Freshly painted, move-in ready two-story home located in a quiet cul-de-sac. VERY LOW HOA of $22.00/month. This home boasts an open floor plan with lots of windows that invite plenty of natural light. The spacious living and dining rooms offer ample space for entertaining. Beautiful set-back kitchen with generous cabinet and countertop space. Large primary bedroom with walk-in closet and private primary bathroom. Spacious guestrooms with lots of closet spaces. The garage is attached but you also have enough driveway space for three additional cars. Great location in a fast-growing Gastonia community with easy access to I85, schools, shopping, restaurants, hiking at Crower's Mountain, and water rafting, boating, and other water sports at the National White Water Center nearby.

NEW*** The Seller is offering a cash concession to replace the KITCHEN REFRIGERATOR with the right offer***
